WEBVTT

00:07:59.271 --> 00:08:03.020
They flee across borders like this one.

00:08:03.020 --> 00:08:06.715
We captured this on the Syrian border to Jordan,

00:08:06.715 --> 00:08:09.675
and this is a typical day.

